  "title": "Temp Junior Med Lab Technologist (6 months/ENTRY LEVEL) - GOVT/Central/Office Hours #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $2500</p><p>Duration: Feb to Sep 2026</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri, Office Hours</p><p>Location: Novena</p><p></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>•  Involve in daily routine lab operations including specimen collection, processing and data recording</p><p>•  Operate equipment and perform appropriate quality control, calibration, and troubleshooting</p><p>•  Attend to request for information (e.g specimen information, lab results and/or materials (e.g blood tubes, slides, blocks)</p><p>•  Maintenance of lab equipment and support research, education and innovation when applicable</p><p>•  Ensure compliance in safety, care and other applicable regulatory requirements of Lab</p><p>•  Assist in clinical practice improvement activities if required</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements: Min Diploma in Biomedical Science or similar</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg </p><p></p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p>allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p>",
